{"tid":2450742,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"果然係全能偶像？TWICE爆JYP出道要先考語言證書","createTime":"2021-03-17T15:23:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-18T12:24:12.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f2ace0f0352407425ae65f0e39240cc231501293","tid":2450742,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T15:23:39.000Z","msg":"做明星都唔易...<br />\n<br />\n韓國K-POP文化在全球都相當有影響力，不少韓團都會加入不同國籍的成員，以便進軍海外市場。當中由韓國娛樂公司JYP推出的女團TWICE除了韓國成員外，團中也有台灣和日本成員，在中文和日文市場都有一定的優勢，外國成員為了在韓國出道都要努力學習韓文。最近TWICE成員擔任了SBS綜藝節目《傳奇舞台》的嘉賓，她們卻大爆原來除了外國成員要面對語言問題外，想在JYP娛樂出道的話，韓國成員也需要學習中文或日文，並需要考外語能力試，引起大批網民的關注。<br />\n<img src=\"https://media-proc.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2021/03/20210317_TWICE_-3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-proc.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2021%2F03%2F20210317_TWICE_-3.jpg&h=444be4c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media-proc.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2021/03/20210317_TWICE_-2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-proc.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2021%2F03%2F20210317_TWICE_-2.jpg&h=88e1e45f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nTWICE是在2015年由4位外國成員和5位韓國成員組成的多國籍組合，她們14日在綜藝節目《傳奇舞台》中講述了自己在出道前的故事，當中主持人問到外國成員在韓國出道有否接受特別的教育，SANA就回答：「我和MOMO上了3年的韓文課，剛剛來韓國的時候完全不懂韓文，只能勉強地向經過的人打招呼。」志效亦提到原來韓國成員也需要學習中文或者日文，她表示：「在我初中的時候，公司就要我考到中文能力考試證書。」娜璉亦補充表示：「如果我們沒有成功考到證書，就不能出道。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://media-proc.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2021/03/20210317_TWICE_-5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-proc.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2021%2F03%2F20210317_TWICE_-5.jpg&h=8224ed46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media-proc.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2021/03/20210317_TWICE_-7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-proc.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2021%2F03%2F20210317_TWICE_-7.jpg&h=c001ea3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media-proc.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2021/03/20210317_TWICE_-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-proc.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2021%2F03%2F20210317_TWICE_-1.jpg&h=066ee3bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不少網民看到節目後表示：「JYP果然很有先見之明！」、「學習外語已經變了成為偶像的必要條件&hellip;」、「甚至要考試，真的很嚴格！」等。<br />\n<img src=\"https://media-proc.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2021/03/20210317_TWICE_-4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-proc.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2021%2F03%2F20210317_TWICE_-4.jpg&h=4e8eedd8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"53bad4620e0f384df38f4c6f58033ed7daeb5921","tid":2450742,"uid":320204,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T15:25:51.000Z","msg":"點解唔學英文？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"473d0c0b1bb186075c6ca295418b07ef2254b724","tid":2450742,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53bad4620e0f384df38f4c6f58033ed7daeb5921","tid":2450742,"uid":320204,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T15:25:51.000Z","msg":"點解唔學英文？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T15:31:21.000Z","msg":"太渣了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2a3285a0311553474e61bbb482207a7e7b24416","tid":2450742,"uid":28765,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T17:08:07.000Z","msg":"點解itzy英文好咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35bc0319eceea7ccc7d4c9b60f599a2edb7ec3dd","tid":2450742,"uid":368098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53bad4620e0f384df38f4c6f58033ed7daeb5921","tid":2450742,"uid":320204,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T15:25:51.000Z","m